OL,3,CPolice investigate funeral directors
OL,4,Cover 'care' of bodies
OL,6,FPolice are investigating a funeral
OL,7,Fdirectors after concerns were raised
OL,8,Fabout its "care for the deceased".
OL,10,Fsaid they had received a call on
OL,11,FWednesday evening about Legacy
OL,12,FIndependent Funeral Directors, which
OL,13,Fruns premises in and the surrounding
OL,14,Farea.
OL,16,FCordons have since been set up at
OL,17,Fthree sites in Hull and Beverley and a
OL,18,Fspecial phone line has been launched
OL,19,Ffor families who may have concerns.
