OL,6,FIn a Facebook post, Hull West and
OL,7,FHessle MP Emma Hardy said she was in
OL,8,Ftouch with the police. She said: "I am
OL,9,Fextremely shocked to have been made
OL,10,Faware that an investigation is taking
OL,11,Fplace into a funeral directors in my
OL,12,Fconstituency.
OL,14,F"My heart goes out to all of the
OL,15,Fworried family members and loved ones.
OL,16,FI can only imagine the distress and
OL,17,Fdevastation that you will be feeling."
