OL,4,Cover 'care' of bodies
OL,6,FAccording to their website, Legacy
OL,7,FIndependent Funeral Directors is a
OL,8,Ffamily-run business, taking "great
OL,9,Fpride in offering professional
OL,10,Fservices and a personal touch from
OL,11,Fstart to finish... offering an
OL,12,Fexceptional level of compassion and
OL,13,Fcare to every client who comes through
OL,14,Fthe doors".
OL,16,FThe website says it has been a member
OL,17,Fof the National Association of Funeral
OL,18,FDirectors (NAFD) since 2011.
OL,20,FThe NAFD said the company gave up its
OL,21,Fmembership in 2021.
