OL,6,FLegacy's website added: "We have a
OL,7,Fprofound belief that a person must be
OL,8,Ftreated with reverence and dignity
OL,9,Fbetween their passing and their
OL,10,Ffuneral, and we always go the extra
OL,11,Fmile to deliver on this principle."
OL,13,FPolice called for people to "refrain
OL,14,Ffrom speculation" about what had
OL,15,Fhappened.
